Analysis in R
  library(gee)
    gee function
    marginal model
  
  library(plm)
    plm function
    fixed-effect and random-effect model, specified with "model" command
  
  library(lme4)
    lmer function
    mixed-effect model
  
  
Analysis in Matlab
  GEEQBOX toolbox
    marginal model. see more at http://www.jstatsoft.org/article/view/v025i14

  fit glme function
    fixed-effect model, mixed-effect model
  
  fitlme function
    mixed-effect model


Analysis in SAS
  PROC GENMODE
    marginal model

  PROC GLM
    fixed-effect model, mixed-effect model with specification of RANDOM statement
  
  PROC MIXED
    mixed-effect model
    
    
    
Note: these packages and functions were not specifically implemented in our manuscript. Rather, this serves as a starting point for a reseracher who prefers using a statistical software other than Stata.
